\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 3. Z. acinoides} L., {\i Sp. Pl.} 22 (1753). Like {\b 2} but stems up to 25 cm; leaves obovate, denticulate towards the apex; verticillasters distant; flowers pedicellate.{\i  • E.C. Spain.} Hs.
\par

